verbose_text: Moreover, when co-expressed with mouse HOIP (mHOIP), mSHARPIN failed to increase the amount of mHOIP, efficiently activate NF-kappaB, or protect cells from TNF-alpha-mediated cytotoxicity in triple KO (TKO) MEFs lacking all LUBAC subunits, whereas mHOIL-1L could do all three (XREF_FIG, XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
